title: Star Wars - Droids
description:
[b]Star Wars: Droids [/b](September 7, 1985 - June 7, 1986), also known as [i]Droids: The Adventures of R2-D2 and C-3PO[/i], is an animated television series that feature the exploits of R2-D2 and C-3PO, the droids who have appeared in all six [i]Star Wars[/i] films. The series takes place between the events depicted in Star Wars Episode III: Revenge of the Sith and Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope.

[b]The Great Heep[/b] was a 48 minute, animated television special that aired on June 7, 1986. It is part of the Star Wars franchise, and was a follow-up to the Star Wars: Droids series.
